RELEASE NOTES


Solutions for Microsoft IIS Web Servers


Enhance Web sites and Web applications with secure, optimized, high-performance
tools. Port80 software exposes control to server-side functionality for 
developers, and streamlines tasks for administrators:

- Increase security by locking down what info you broadcast and blocking intruders
with ServerMask and ServerDefender

- Protect your intellectual property by preventing hotlinking with LinkDeny

- Improve performance: compress pages and manage cache controls for faster load time
and bandwidth savings with CacheRight, httpZip, and ZipEnable

- Upgrade Web development tools: Negotiate content based on device, language,
or other parameters with PageXchanger, and tighten code with w3compiler.


	
      Security
             
         + ServerMask (4.1.0)
		- Server anonymization for enhanced security

         + LinkDeny (1.1.3)
		- Anti-leeching and access control
	
	 + ServerDefender (1.4.0 / coming soon)
		- Advanced Web application firewalls
	        

      Performance
             
         + CacheRight (3.0.5)
		- Cache management for devlopers

         + HTTPzip (3.8.9)
		- Advanced HTTP compression for speed and bandwith savings

         + ZipEnable (3.02)
		- Advanced HTTP compression for IIS 6.0


      Development
             
         + W3Compiler (1.1.2)
		- Compress and obfusacte HTML, CSS, and Javascript

         + PageXchanger (2.0.06)
		- Content negotiation & Migration
